WITH del_leases AS (
            DELETE FROM leases
            WHERE message_id = $2
        ),
        del_failed AS (
            DELETE FROM attempts_failed
            WHERE message_id = $2
        ),
        ins_dead AS (
            INSERT INTO attempts_dead (message_id, dead_at)
            VALUES ($2, $3)
        )
        INSERT INTO errors (id, message_id, reported_at, error)
        VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4)
